      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 23:54:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊拉克的复杂信息让OPEC+成为焦点，油价小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价小幅走低，因交易商展望欧佩克+供应政策会议，而伊拉克就其立场发出了复杂的信息。]]></description>
